        260
      ],
      "continueOnFail": true
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Flow E \u2014 Lead Acquisition\n\nThis flow accepts incoming acquisition leads via webhook, posts them to the local acquisition service, and allows the service to enrich and auto-ingest qualified records into the Google Sheet CRM.\n\nUse this when you want to collect leads from web forms, Zapier, Apollo, or other partner systems without touching the outbound voice flow.\n\nEnv vars:\n- `LEAD_ACQUISITION_URL` \u2014 e.g. `http://localhost:8200`\n- `LEAD_COLLECTOR_URL` \u2014 e.g. `http://localhost:8100`\n- `LUSHA_API_KEY` \u2014 optional for enrichment\n- `ACQUISITION_AUTO_INGEST_MIN_SCORE` \u2014 numeric threshold, default `65`\n\nPayload example:\n{\n  \"name\": \"Jane Doe\",\n  \"phone\": \"+14155551234\",\n  \"email\": \"jane@example.com\",\n  \"company\": \"Acme Inc.\",\n  \"title\": \"VP Sales\",\n  \"linkedin_url\": \"https://www.linkedin.com/in/janedoe\",\n  \"source\": \"webhook\"\n}\n",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "note",
      "name": "Flow E Notes",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        240,
        40
      ]
    }
  ],
